SSL aur TLS – Bilkul Basic Samjho

Problem kya thi?
Jab internet naya-naya tha:
          Data plain text me jaata tha
          Koi bhi beech me padh sakta tha
          Password, login sab dikh jaata tha 
Is problem ka solution chahiye tha.


SSL kyu aaya?
SSL ka full form: Secure Sockets Layer
SSL bola:
“Browser aur Server ke beech
data ko lock kar dete hain”
Shuru me ye kaam chal gaya.

Par SSL me problem aa gayi
Time ke saath:
Hackers smart ho gaye
SSL ke bugs mil gaye
Data todna possible ho gaya
Isliye:  SSL 2.0, 3.0 band kar diye gaye





TLS aaya (SSL ka bada bhai)
TLS ka full form: Transport Layer Security
TLS bola:
“Main SSL ka improved version hoon
aur zyada secure hoon.”

TLS ne:
Strong locks use kiye
Fast connection banaya
Old problems hata di


Aaj ke time me kya use hota hai?
Browser → TLS use karta hai
Server → TLS use karta hai
HTTPS = TLS enabled connection

Log bolte hain:
“SSL lagaya hai”
Par asal me: TLS chal raha hota hai




Fresher ke liye 5 super simple points
1. SSL purana hai
2. TLS new aur safe hai
3. HTTPS ka matlab TLS 
